clinics.name: University of California, Davis Family Planning
clinics.website_note: UC Davis Health's Family Planning Center in Sacramento is led by a team of Obstetrician-Gynecologists, who specialize in family planning and women’s reproductive health, including contraception, sterilization, miscarriage and abortion. There is no other group of physicians in the Sacramento region with the same level of training and expertise. At the Family Planning Center, we believe that every woman deserves nonjudgmental, confidential, and compassionate attention to her unique needs throughout her reproductive life. We will partner with you to decide which birth control options are best, based upon your lifestyle, family planning goals, and existing medical conditions. We provide counseling and care for women in need of an elective abortion, treatment for miscarriage or fetal death, and termination due to medical reasons. UC Davis Health's Family Planning Center staff, along with all the physicians in Obstetrics and Gynecology, are invested in helping every woman regardless of her choices or needs during pregnancy.
